-- Walgreen offers to buy Longs for $3 bln including debt
-- 
-- Fri Sep 12, 2008 7:58pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/09/12/us-walgreen-longs-idUSHAR28620120080912

 

 (Reuters) - Walgreen Co ( WAG.N ) said on Friday that it has proposed to acquire Longs Drug Stores Corp for $75 per share in cash transaction. 

 * Says approximate $3 billion proposal * Says approximate $3 billion proposal, includes assumption of debt * Says its offer is subject to regulatory review and completion of due diligence * Says offer represents $3.50 per share premium over cash price under deal proposed by CVS Caremark Corp ( CVS.N )